"Optional fields can be omitted. Module names passed for filtering are not "
"regex-escaped.  For example:  .. code-block:: python      @pytest.mark."
"filterwarnings(\"ignore:.*usage will be deprecated.*:"
"DeprecationWarning\")     def test_foo():         ..."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/reference/reference.rst:157
msgid ""
