msgid "**Tutorial**: :ref:`scoped-marking`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/reference/reference.rst:1052
msgid ""
"Can be declared at the **global** level in *test modules* to apply one or "
"more :ref:`marks <marks ref>` to all test functions and methods. Can be "
"either a single mark or a list of marks (applied in left-to-right order)."
